text: George Morgan (7 July 1844 - 17 July 1896) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1874/75. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1844 births Category:1896 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
